WEBVTT

00:02:58.875 --> 00:03:03.589
but also because each one represents
a special interest group,

00:03:04.233 --> 00:03:08.622
a special interest group
that used to advocate for their concerns

00:03:08.646 --> 00:03:09.811
one at a time.

00:03:09.835 --> 00:03:14.934
They did not see the, what I call,
"co-benefits" of urban form

00:03:14.958 --> 00:03:17.433
that allows them to join with others.

00:03:17.457 --> 00:03:19.045
So, land consumption:

00:03:19.069 --> 00:03:21.883
environmentalists are really
concerned about this,

00:03:21.907 --> 00:03:23.092
so are farmers;

00:03:23.696 --> 00:03:25.918
there's a whole range of people,

00:03:25.942 --> 00:03:29.329
and, of course, neighborhood groups
that want open space nearby.

00:03:29.861 --> 00:03:31.947
The sprawl version of California